Alert;As per public address by the Prime Minister, India will be on lockdown till 14th April. No public transport will be available in Telangana during this period including buses, autos, and cabs. Public can go out for essential commodities during daylight hours only. During dark hours there is full curfew and those without curfew passes will not be allowed. Please call 100 (police) or 104 (coronavirus helpline) in case of emergency.
